&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a Team Secretary to work as part of the Secretarial Team at Cannock Eye Centre to provide a comprehensive secretarial service to the Consultants and their team. Principle duties will include word processing of digital dictation, administration work surrounding the patient attendance, enquires and covering for colleagues during absence. We require a highly motivated person with a proven ability to prioritise multiple tasks. You should possess a minimum of OCR 3 or equivalent word processing and be a competent Audio Typist. Knowledge of medical terminology is essential.&lt;/p&gt;
